# Building A Quest

## Purpose

This guide defines how quest artifacts are built.

It exists to keep detailed quest-construction rules out of the stable source-of-truth docs while still preserving a repeatable production standard.

This file is about production method, not campaign law.

When in conflict, this document only governs its owned area.

